INSTRUCTIONS:

I know usually demos and intros are not interactive but this is an exception.
STAGE 1: Bouncing ball
- a : blow wind to the left
- s : stop blowing wind
- d : blow wind to the right
STAGE 2: Rotating cube
- use wasd for moving the cube around the screen
- q : shrink the cube
- r : expand the cube
STAGE 3: Friction
- d : move balls to the right
- a : move balls to the left
STAGE 4: Attraction
- wasd will move the big ball around the screen, little ball will be attracted to the big ball
ALL STAGES:
- esc or left mouse button: return to the OS
- v : the hidden part kicks in